title: Zerto VPG RPO
agents: linux
catalog: hw/app/zerto
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors if a VPG meets the SLA specification for the journal history
 or the RPO SLA setting. If the SLA specification is not met, the check will be
 {CRIT}. If the VPG is initializing, in failover or move operations, being deleted
 or recovered, the check will be {WARN}.
 The VPG data is piggybacked to each VM.

inventory:
 One service is created per VPG.
